item.title: CVE-2023-29108|2024-08-02T14:00:15.410Z -- sap -- abap%20platform%20and%20sap%20web%20dispatcher
item.description: The IP filter in ABAP Platform and SAP Web Dispatcher - versions WEBDISP 7.85, 7.89, KERNEL 7.85, 7.89, 7.91, may be vulnerable by erroneous IP netmask handling. This may enable access to backend applications from unwanted sources.
